title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters' dialog
description: When trying to view the report parameters in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog, the default values are not displayed.
OB: Default values are not shown in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog
EB: The default values for report parameters should be displayed in the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog
SR:
1. Open the 'Show Report Parameters' dialog.
2. Check if the default values for report parameters are displayed correctly.
